title: [Arahbella's Outfitting]
[Arahbella's General Store]
[Arahbella's Magic Shoppe]
description: Enclosed by brilliant cut-glass walls, the shop features a tiered alabaster fountain in the center of its celadon marble floor.  An oil-filled silver sconce hangs under the vaulted ceiling.  Right near the front is a large carved haon counter and a vine-carved mahogany table.
